description: To pursue its investment objective, the fund invests, under normal market circumstances, at least 80% of its net assets (plus any borrowings for investment purposes) in component securities of the index. The index is designed to track the performance of a strategy that seeks to provide risk-managed exposure to exchange-traded funds ("ETFs") that investment primarily in high yield debt instruments.
name: Donoghue Forlines Tactical High Yield ETF
